ALICE-DB Open Core License
===========================

Copyright (c) 2024-2026 Moroya Sakamoto

================================================================================
Open Core Strategy
================================================================================

ALICE-DB uses an Open Core licensing model with hybrid strategy:

| Product                | License        | Description                          |
|------------------------|----------------|--------------------------------------|
| ALICE-DB Core          | MIT            | Free and open source                 |
| ALICE-DB Server        | BSL 1.1        | Source available, DBaaS restricted   |
| ALICE-DB Enterprise    | Commercial     | Annual contract                      |

================================================================================
